Overview

Here we will recapitulate the analyses done for the manuscript. These are the analyses on the 16S sequencing data on samples collected from gut-on-chip in different O2 concentrations (please revert to publication for details on experimental setup.) All code is available on Github. This report was prepared using rmarkdown and knitted into HTML using knitr.

Data

Data was processed with QIIME and loaded into R using the phyloseq package. Data was subsequently transform into the tidy format using functions in the tidyverse package.

Richness analysis

Richness analysis was performed with the phyloseq::estimate_richness function. Beta diversity was performed with PERMANOVA using the adonis function in the vegan package.
